git clone => github bata folder afno ma launa lai use garne yo 
git status => code ko status herna lai kam lagcha 
git add => naya or change gareko file add garne 
git add . => sab file ekaichoti add garna lai
git commit=> commit garne code record garne code 
git push=> upload garne github ma 
git init => git initialize garna lai

Work flow => github ma repo banaune paila ani git clone garne ani changes garne file ma ani git add . garne 
git commit -m "msg" garne ani git push -u origin main gardine push huncha 

git branches
git branch => to check branch
git branch -M main (to rename branch)
git checkout -b "branchname"  (naya branch banauna lai)
git branch -d "branchname" (delete garna branch lai )

merging code

git diff "branchname" (compare garne differences )
git merge "branchname" (merge garna duita branch haru)
git pull origin main (code launa afno ma )
git push origin "branch name" garne branch ko push hanna lai
git merge (branch merge garne) natra pull request garne 

//undoing changes
git log garera sab commit herna milcha 
jun add va tara commit vachaina tesko lai use garne =git reset filename or git reset (dherai file lai yo)
add garera commit ni garyo vane tesko lai yo use garne= git reset HEAD~1 or (dherai commit lai reset garna lai) 
git reset <commit hash> hash chai git log garera leraune  git reset --hard <hash>